data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS OFFERING A $5,000 SELLER CONCESSION! Welcome to the epitome of luxury living in the exclusive gated community of Westwinds Lonestar, located in the highly sought-after neighborhood of Alamo Ranch. This magnificent 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home spans a generous 2,320 square feet, offering an exceptional blend of elegance and comfort. Upon entering the grand foyer, you'll be captivated by the abundance of natural light streaming through the large windows, illuminating the stunning crown moulding that adorns the ceilings. The living room becomes the heart of the residence, boasting a cozy fireplace that exudes warmth and charm, creating the perfect ambiance for gatherings with family and friends. For those seeking a space for entertainment and leisure, look no further than the thoughtfully designed media room, where you can indulge in your favorite movies and shows in style. Additionally, a spacious study provides the ideal setting for a home office, creating a perfect balance between work and relaxation. This home's open-concept design seamlessly integrates the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it an entertainer's dream. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's delight, equipped with a gas cooktop and built-in oven for culinary excellence. The tiled backsplash adds a touch of sophistication to the space, while the breakfast bar and eat-in breakfast area offer flexible dining options for everyday meals or special occasions. The stainless-steel appliances lend a modern touch to the kitchen's allure. The tranquil master bedroom retreat beckons with its tray ceilings and large windows that bathe the room in natural light. The walk-in closet provides ample storage space for all your belongings. The master en-suite is a sanctuary of relaxation, featuring a luxurious garden tub, a generously sized walk-in shower, and separate vanities, creating a spa-like atmosphere in the privacy of your own home. Step outside to the backyard and discover a spacious covered patio, where you can bask in the fresh air and enjoy dining and outdoor activities. The mature trees provide shade and charm, and the privacy fence ensures a serene and secluded setting, making it an ideal place for relaxation and outdoor entertaining. With a 2-car garage, this home offers convenience and practicality for modern living. The gated community of Westwinds Lonestar adds an extra layer of security and exclusivity, creating a true sense of community and comfort. Conveniently located near JBSA-Lackland, VA Medical Clinic, Seaworld, Six Flags, shopping, restaurants, and all major highways.  Don't miss this exceptional opportunity to call this exquisite residence your own. Experience the height of luxury living in Alamo Ranch's Westwinds Lonestar. Schedule a viewing today and take the first step toward making this dream home yours. Welcome to a life of unparalleled elegance and sophistication!
